column1: #Text=Gosnold is a town in Massachusetts off of Cape Cod encompassing the nine Elizabeth Islands , including Cuttyhunk Island , Naushon Island , Pasque Island , Nashawena Island and some adjacent smaller islands that stretch out from Woods Hole village of Falmouth .
#Text=Gosnold has the smallest population of any Massachusetts town .
#Text=Gosnold separates Vineyard Sound from Buzzards Bay .
#Text=The southernmost island of Cuttyhunk has most of the island chain 's population and is the only island that is not entirely private .
#Text=Less than one hundred people live there year round .
#Text=Many boaters enjoy visiting the cozy harbor on day trips .
#Text=Gosnold 's entertainment is all provided by nature .
#Text=Deer roam the island almost as if tame , but there are no movie theatres , nightclubs or tennis courts .
#Text=Alert II , Fisherman 's Wharf , Pier 3 , New Bedford , Phone : +1 508-992-1432.
#Text=Bayside Air , New Bedford Regional Airport , New Bedford , Phone : +1 508-636-3762.
#Text=Cuttyhunk has a famous harbor for its many sailboats .
#Text=Golf carts are the main mode of transportation .
#Text=This is not the place to go to enjoy night life .
#Text=Take long relaxing walks to the beach , to the old ship wreck , or the historic war fort ( used to fight the British ) .
#Text=It is the charm of the houses , the Inn , and the quaint little stores , that keep bringing people back .
#Text=Go on a fishing charter from Fisherman 's Point .
#Text=12 rooms with shared baths , also one cottage and one upper story suite with a great view .
#Text=This is the only lodging on the island .
#Text=Cuttyhunk , Pasque , Nashawena , & Penikese Islands - 13A Broadway , Cuttyhunk , MA 02713 - +1 508-994-7392
#Text=The other islands in Gosnold use the Woods Hole post office - 16 Water Street , Woods Hole , MA 02543 - +1 508-548-0604
#Text=You may be dependent on the landlines because of weak ( if any ) cellular phone reception .
#Text=There are also some payphones on Cuttyhunk .
#Text=If you have enough in your budget , using a satellite phone could also work .
#Text=Cuttyhunk Island has an island-wide Wi-Fi network .
